Class CCogniton

    • civilisation.individu.cognitons.CCogniton

  • public class CCogniton
extends java.lang.Object
    CCogniton is the combination of a Cogniton and a hashmap to store data about the cogniton Only CCogniton are instantiated after initialization. No more NCogniton.
